channel.title: New headphones
channel.description:
So I'm looking for some new headphones, currently own 2 pairs of skullcandies, one in ear (ink'd 2010), and one pair of shattered grey on ear (hesh) headphones.
Looking for something of a little higher quality, budget of around £100.
I listen to dubstep primarily, particularly Skrillex, Feed Me, Spor, Deadmau5, Chasing Shadows, Noisia, Flux Pavilion, Foreign Beggars, Example, etc, mostly pretty heavy stuff.
Been looking at some of the AKG products, they seem ite, anyone had some personal experience with them? [url=http://www.amazon.co.uk/AKG-Acoustics-518-DJ-Headphones/dp/B000ISP3M4/ref=pd_cp_ce_1]http://www.amazon.co.uk/AKG-Acoustics-518-DJ-Headphones/dp/B000ISP3M4/ref=pd_cp_ce_1[/url] Also, how much better would these be compared to my £35 candy hesh pair?
Meanwhile, listen to this: [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tJcm4uoCzW8]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tJcm4uoCzW8[/url] Little old but whatever, opinions plz.
